name: WiregrassAlerts
0:
”Alexa, launch Wiregrass Alerts”
”Which cities are supported?”
”Alerts in Dothan?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wiregrass alerts
des: The wiregrass area is known for its humidity and also for receiving powerful storms capable of producing tornadoes. To be aware of any severe weather alerts such as Tornado Warnings or Tornado Watches, the Wiregrass Alert Skill will inform you what the alerts for the current moment are.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
